  m_Name: ML_Intro_Mischievous
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: There you are. I was beginning to think the interesting one had changed her mind.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: Interesting, or troubled?
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: With people like you, it is usually the same thing.
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: Sit. The cards are kinder to people who stop pretending.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Then deal.
